item.description:
Energetic transmission from divine beings
with Helene Olsen
Friday March 11, 7:30-9:00 p.m. $20
Open to all - no attendee limit.  Bring family& friends!
You won't want to miss this - rsvp at www.AngelsLighthouse.com

Who are you? Where are you?  Do things "happen" to you more than you consciously create them? Open your heart and mind to your own multi-dimensional existence as Helene discusses finding your own true self and creating the highest aspects for your life. This interactive event is meant to raise your vibration, inspire your next moves forward, and open you to your limitless nature. Divine beings will channel messages to the group through Helene. In addition, Helene has an amazing capacity as a conduit for Divine energy and will be allowing this magnificent energy to flow through her and extend to all in attendance.
item.why: Greetings, meditators! As ones interested in higher vibration, you may want to join us Friday March 11 with Helene Olsen as she transmits loving and healing energy from divine beings. She will also channel messages for the group. 7:30-9 pm, $20
